FROM deepseek-ocr:latest

# OCR-optimized parameters for document processing
# Based on DeepSeek-OCR Local Guide and official recommendations

# Deterministic text extraction (critical for OCR accuracy)
PARAMETER temperature 0.0

# Maximum context window for long documents and complex layouts
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192

# Prevent hallucinations and repetitive text
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1

# Timeout handling - allows longer inference for large/complex documents
PARAMETER num_predict 4096

# System prompt for OCR-specialized behavior
SYSTEM You are an expert OCR assistant. Extract text accurately, preserve layouts and structure, and handle multilingual content. Focus on accuracy over speed.
